## ğŸ’¡ Slash Commands Available

### `/resume` - Resume from Last Session
- Reads all memory bank files
- Shows what was done previously
- Asks what to work on next
- **Use at**: Session start OR when picking new task

### `/status` - Quick Status Check
- Shows current task and recent progress
- Lists blockers and next steps
- Does NOT ask what to work on
- **Use at**: Mid-session check-ins

### `/handoff` - Prepare for IDE Switch
- Updates memory bank with final status
- Reminds you to commit and push
- Prepares context for other IDEs
- **Use at**: End of session, before switching IDEs

### `/start` - Start New Session
- Initializes session state
- Reads memory bank
- Sets up initial context

